<html>
<head>
<title>Strucutral Annotation</title>
<script src="/js/json.js"  type="text/javascript"></script>
<script src="/js/eucap.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
<link href="/css/eucap.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">
<style type="text/css">
.feature { text-align:center; }
</style>
</head>

<body>
<form name="back_to_annotation" method="post" action="/cgi-bin/eucap.pl">
<input type="hidden" name="action" value="annotate">
<input type="submit" name="back" value="Back to Main Annotation Page">
</form>
<h2>Structural Annotation for Locus: <TMPL_VAR NAME="locus"></h2>

<p style="width:640px;background-color:#F4FFE3;padding:10px;">Useful links for structural annotation - <br>
<a href="http://deepc2.psi.iastate.edu/aat/align/align.html">Iowa
  State AAT server</a>
<p>

<img id="ca_image" border="0" src="<TMPL_VAR NAME="img_path">" usemap="#<TMPL_VAR NAME="map_name">">

<p class="small">Exon Coordinate info - Roll the mouse cursor over the
  exon features above to display their coordinates:</p>
<p>
<form name="subfeature_coords">
  <td>Rel Start:</td>
  <td><input type="text" name="rel_end5" value="" size="6"></td>
  <td>Rel End:</td>
  <td><input type="text" name="rel_end3" value="" size="6"></td>

  <td>Abs Start:</td>
  <td><input type="text" name="abs_end5" value="" size="10"></td>
  <td>Abs End:</td>
  <td><input type="text" name="abs_end3" value="" size="10"></td>
</form>
<p>

<form action="/cgi-bin/eucap.pl" method="post"
      name="struct_anno"> 

<input type="hidden" name="action" id="action" value="struct_anno">

<!-- hidden inputs for locus info -->
<input type="hidden" name="locus" value="<TMPL_VAR NAME="locus">">
<input type="hidden" name="locus_type" value="<TMPL_VAR NAME="locus_type">">
<input type="hidden" name="locus_seq_id" value="<TMPL_VAR NAME="locus_seq_id">">
<input type="hidden" name="locus_start" value="<TMPL_VAR NAME="locus_start">">
<input type="hidden" name="locus_stop" value="<TMPL_VAR NAME="locus_stop">">
<input type="hidden" name="locus_strand"
      value="<TMPL_VAR NAME="locus_strand">">
<!-- end hidden inputs -->
<p class="small" style="width:600px;">
Modify the gene structure using the table below and press "View
Annotation" to view the community annotation model above. The coding
and translated sequence will be displayed below. Press "Submit
Annotation" to save the gene model to the database.
</p>
<table id="ca" border="1" width="640px" cellspacing="0"
       cellpadding="5px" class="data">
<thead>
<tr>
  <th>Delete Feature</th>
  <th>Feat Type</th>
<th>Start</th>
<th>Stop</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody id="ca_table_body">
  <TMPL_LOOP NAME="ca_anno_loop">
    <tr class="add"><td colspan="4" align="right"><input type="button" name="add_feature"
    value="Add Feature" onclick="addFeature(this)"></td></tr>
    <tr class="feature">
      <td><input type="button" name="delete" value="Delete" onclick="deleteFeature(this)"></td>
      <td>
        <select name="type">
         
            <option
            value="CDS" <TMPL_IF
            NAME="CDS">selected="selected"</TMPL_IF> >CDS</option>
           
          <option value="UTR" <TMPL_UNLESS NAME="CDS">selected="selected"</TMPL_UNLESS>>UTR</option>
        </select>
      </td>
      <td><input type="text" name="start" size="10" value="<TMPL_VAR NAME="start">"></td>
      <td><input type="text" name="stop" size="10" value="<TMPL_VAR NAME="stop">"></td>
    </tr>
  </TMPL_LOOP>
  <tr class="add"><td colspan="4" align="right"><input type="button" name="add_feature"
    value="Add Feature" onclick="addFeature(this)"></td></tr>
</tbody>
<table>

<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="5px" width="640px">
<tr>
<td align="center">
<input type="button" name="view_annotation" value="View Annotation"
    onclick="viewAnnotation()">
</td>
<td>
<input type="button" name="submit_annotation"
 value="Submit Annotation To Database" onclick="submitAnnotation()">
</td align="center">
</table>
<input type="hidden" name="model_json" value="" id="model_json">

</form>

<TMPL_VAR NAME="map">
</body>
</html>
